<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Physical Therapy and Rehabilitation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 103</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition for Healthy Living</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">This courseincludes the definition of nutrition and importance of food groups, macro nutrients, micro nutrients, water and drinks, the importance of nutrition in the Prevention of diseases, obesity, popular diets, eating disorders, diseases, nutrition, physical activity, and nutrition covers.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=420805&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Physical Therapy and Rehabilitation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 104</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">History of Science / History of World Science</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">This course examines the development of sciences and the relations between science and society since the beginning of humanity. In particular, the course will examine the change in the approach to science and the socialization of science since the first scientific endeavors. Science approach to change over time ozerklesmes Sciences Science-the relationship between politics and religion, the relationship between science and Technology, Social Sciences, the development of the socialization of science, groundbreaking, paradigm-wrecker important scientific discoveries and theories, and training of scientists working methods, the relationship between science and culture are among the main topics of the course.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=420806&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Physical Therapy and Rehabilitation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 105</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Story in Turkish Literature</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Basic features of the story genre, the transformation of the story genre in the period from the Tanzimat period to the Republican period and the study of selected stories from Turkish literature.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=420807&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Physical Therapy and Rehabilitation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 107</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Ottoman Cultural History</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">It includes recognizing and examining the cultural heritage of the early Ottoman period, the Classical period and the Modern period.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=420809&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Physical Therapy and Rehabilitation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 108</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Health, Sports, Exercise</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">To teach some information about physical fitness, development and protection.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=420810&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Physical Therapy and Rehabilitation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 110</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Culture, Body and Gender Roles</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Behaviours and gender roles that find reflection in the human body are shaped according to the society, culture, socioeconomic class and political environment experienced and can be changed according to need. These behaviors are influenced by power ideologies, social movements, social crises, and the current historical period.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=420811&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Physical Therapy and Rehabilitation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 111</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Music Throughout History II</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">This course explains the topics such as concert videos starting with 18. 20th century music, currents and composers.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=420879&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Physical Therapy and Rehabilitation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 113</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Introduction to Philosophy</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">What Is Philosophy? What Are The Characteristics Of Philosophical Thought? What Are The Basic Philosophical Concepts? The Relationship Between Philosophy And Knowledge, The Relationship Between Philosophy And Science, The Relationship Between Philosophy And Existence, The Relationship Between Philosophy And Morality, The Relationship Between Philosophy And Religion.</Data></Cell>
