<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 151</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Digital Photography and Photo Processing Techniques</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Definition of photography, history of photography from film to digital and its artistic context
Classification of the camera according to different criteria
Basic camera components
Auxiliary equipment and accessories in photography
Camera Basic Settings
Light - exposure and equipment in photography
Composition and elements in photography
Types Of Photography
Mobile photography
Photo processing programs and processing techniques
Archiving and digital storage</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=420747&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
