<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Throughout the lessons, these stereotypes of health discourses will be discussed from different perspectives. In the following lessons, students will be asked to choose a text or material to discuss these stereotypes of health discourses.</Data></Cell>
