<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Physical Therapy and Rehabilitation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">FZT 133</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Case Presentation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Rheumatoid arthritis, Parkinson&apos;s disease, Duchenne muscular dystrophy, Achilles tendinitis, Pes planus, What is orthosis-what are the uses, Physiotherapy in diabetes, Physiotherapy in menopause, Fibromyalgia, Geriatric rehabilitation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=420875&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Physical Therapy and Rehabilitation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">FZT 149</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Career Planning for Physiotherapists</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">29.09.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">This course addresses the concept of career and the importance of career planning during the student process. It aims to help students develop their self-awareness and self-assessment skills, analyze opportunities and threats by recognizing their strengths and areas for improvement. It also covers short- and long-term planning, time management, the concept of the future “you,” and the resume (CV) preparation process.
It focuses on the role of mindfulness-based awareness and habit change in career management. Different work environments in the field of physical therapy and rehabilitation are introduced, and interviews and field experiences regarding the roles of physical therapists in these environments are shared. The course is supported by brainstorming, discussions, and assignment presentations.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=420853&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Physical Therapy and Rehabilitation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ATA 102</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Ataturk&apos;s Principles and History of Revolution II</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">22.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Independence War, founding of the Turkish Grand National Assembly, international treaties, peace process, establishment of the Republic, Ataturk’s principles and revolutions</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=420903&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
