<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2,5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Overview of Spinal Cord Injuries- Injury formation mechanisms, anatomical evaluation,
Rehabilitation Principles of Spinal Cord Injuries- Clinical syndromes in injury, Assessment methods, Functional rehabilitation by level,
Rehabilitation Practices in Spinal Cord Injuries- Practical Application,
Traumatic Brain Injuries and Rehabilitation,
Brain Tumors and Rehabilitation,
Motor Neuron Diseases and Rehabilitation,
Motor Junction Diseases and Rehabilitation,
Polio and Post-Polio Syndromes and Rehabilitation,
Rehabilitation in Sensory Perception Disorders,
Cognitive Rehabilitation,
Peripheral Neuropathies and Rehabilitation,
Neuropathic Pain and Rehabilitation,
Bladder and Bowel Rehabilitation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=420909&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Physical Therapy and Rehabilitation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">FZT 342</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Pediatric Rehabilitation II</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+1+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2,5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Introduction to Vojta Treatment Method, How to Apply Vojta Treatment Method, Congenital Brachial Plexus Paralysis and Rehabilitation, Torticolis and Rehabilitation, Neuroleural Tube Defects and Rehabilitation, Muscular Diseases (Muscular Dystrophies and Atrophies), Evaluation in Muscle Diseases - Apparatus, Physiotherapy in Down Syndrome, Juvenile Rheumatoid Arthritis and Rehabilitation, Peripheral Neuropathies (Guilla Barre) and Rehabilitation, Rehabilitation of Oncological Diseases in Children, Evaluation of Walking in Children, Balance and Coordination Education, Approach to Disabled Children and Their Family</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=420919&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
