<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Physical Therapy and Rehabilitation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">FZT 344</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Special Topics in Physiotherapy</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">22.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Facial Paralysis and Rehabilitation, Burn Rehabilitation, Cancer Rehabilitation, Obesity Rehabilitation, Physiotherapy in Headaches, Geriatric Rehabilitation, Elastic Banding</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=420954&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Physical Therapy and Rehabilitation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">FZT 346</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Home and Intensive Care Rehabilitation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">22.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The concept of home care, the duties of physiotherapists in home care services, the place and importance of physiotherapy and rehabilitation in home care, planning and implementation, the pathophysiology and rehabilitation of critical illness and respiratory failure, evaluation in intensive care patients, the use of life support equipment in clinical monitoring and evaluation, mechanical ventilation, physiotherapy and rehabilitation practices</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=420872&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Physical Therapy and Rehabilitation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">FZT 348</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Rehabilitation in Women&apos;s Health and Diseases</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">22.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Female Reproductive Organ Anatomy and Physiology, Normal Pregnancy and Pregnancy Complications, Assessment in Obstetric Rehabilitation, Obstetric Rehabilitation, Postpartum Rehabilitation and Follow-up of Mother and Baby, Physiotherapy and Rehabilitation in Urinary Incontinence, Lymphedema and Assessment, Physical Therapy and Rehabilitation in Lymphedema, Physical Therapy and Rehabilitation in Pelvic Organ Prolapse, Physical Therapy and Rehabilitation in Fecal Incontinence, Physical Therapy and Rehabilitation in Pelvic Pain, Physical Therapy and Rehabilitation in Sexual
Dysfunction</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=420798&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Physical Therapy and Rehabilitation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">FZT 362</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Research and Social Responsibility Project in Physiotherapy III</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Collecting data related to the project, performing statistical calculation and project presentation.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=420799&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Physical Therapy and Rehabilitation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">FZT 364</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Biopsychosocial Approach</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">22.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">This course aims to teach evidence-based approaches used in the assessment and management of chronic pain by addressing the physiological, psychological, and social dimensions of pain within the biopsychosocial model.
Intervention methods such as fear-avoidance behaviors, belief systems, cognitive functional therapy, and graded exposure are examined using case examples. Additionally, the importance of multidisciplinary teamwork in chronic pain is emphasized and reinforced with clinical application examples.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=420792&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Physical Therapy and Rehabilitation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">FZT 427</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Clinical Practice II</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">7</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">0+28+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">14</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">22</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17.03.2026</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">All theoretical and practical courses taken during the undergraduate program must be applied in practice in 3-week-long sessions under the supervision of advisors.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=420920&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Physical Therapy and Rehabilitation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">FZT 441</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Clinical Problem Solving in Physiotherapy I</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">7</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Evaluation on neurological, orthopedic, pediatric, pulmonary and sports rehabilitation cases and discussion of treatments.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=420793&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Physical Therapy and Rehabilitation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">FZT 422</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Management and Organization in Physiotherapy</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">7</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">22.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Management-Manager-Organization Concepts, Management functions, Management processes and leadership, Characteristics of health management, Hospital businesses, Patient safety management, Team concept and motivation, Total quality management and accreditation practices, Legal texts and legislation regarding the physiotherapy profession, National and international physiotherapy profession and non-governmental organizations are included in the course.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=420833&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Physical Therapy and Rehabilitation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">FZT 433</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Technological Rehabilitation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">7</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Information about technological approaches that can be used in physiotherapy and rehabilitation (virtual reality, video games, tele-rehabilitation, wearable technologies, mobile applications, robotic applications and mobility aids).</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=420932&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
