<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">In the field of physiotherapy and rehabilitation, the subject of research is determined with the lecturer within the framework of the student&apos;s interests. The student reports to the lecturer about the researches and articles he / she teaches at the specified time every week. The course ends with the presentation of the researched articles at the end of the semester for the evaluation of the instructor.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=420930&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
