<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Students will be able to describe themselves and people around them using simple adjectives, ask and answer basic questions to exchange personal information, and engage in short conversations.</Data></Cell>
