<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Students are capable of describing family members and relationships, as well as daily routines — both their own and others’ — through written and spoken communication. They also comprehend short reading passages on these topics.</Data></Cell>
