<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Turkish Language II</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">By evaluating the phenomenon of language in its various dimensions, such as language-thought, language-individual, language-society, and language-culture, each student understands how important language really is.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=420905&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
