<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The demonic other (1960’s – 1970’s)
Reading: Barbara Creed: “Woman as Possessed Monster: The Exorcist.” in The Monstrous Feminine.31-42. (Available on-line on Google Books)
Film: The Exorcist (William Friedkin, 1968), Rosemary’s Baby (Polanski, 1968)</Data></Cell>
